# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# GLOBAL COCO EXPORTS — ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the values.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── Resend (Transactional Email) ────────────────────────────
# Get your API key at: https://resend.com/api-keys
RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxx

# The 'from' domain for sending emails.
# For testing on Resend free tier, leave as "onboarding@resend.dev"
# For production, verify your domain at https://resend.com/domains
# RESEND_FROM_DOMAIN=globalcocoexports.com
RESEND_FROM_DOMAIN=onboarding@resend.dev

# ─── Admin Notification Recipient ────────────────────────────
# All RFQ and enquiry notifications are sent here.
ADMIN_EMAIL=santhoshganesan9972@gmail.com

# ─── Company Details ─────────────────────────────────────────
COMPANY_NAME=Global Coco Exports
COMPANY_EMAIL=info@globalcocoexports.com
COMPANY_WHATSAPP=+91XXXXXXXXXX

# ─── Supabase (Database) ─────────────────────────────────────
# Get these from your Supabase project dashboard:
# Project Settings → API → Project URL & Service Role Secret
SUPABASE_URL=https://xxxxxxxxxxxx.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...

# ─── Google reCAPTCHA (Optional — recommended) ───────────────
# Uncomment and add your keys for additional spam protection.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_RECAPTCHA_SITE_KEY=6Lc...
# RECAPTCHA_SECRET_KEY=6Lc...

# ─── Google Analytics (Optional) ─────────────────────────────
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

# ─── Microsoft Clarity (Optional) ────────────────────────────
# NEXT_PUBLIC_CLARITY_ID=xxxxxxxxxx

# ─── Google Search Console (Optional) ────────────────────────
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_VERIFICATION=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
